HEADWORD: Shook
<hw>Shook</hw> <pr>(sh⟦oocr⟧k)</pr>, <def><pos>imp.</pos> & <mark>obs.</mark>  or <mark>poet.</mark> <pos>p. p.</pos> of <er>Shake</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
